{
  "3188910": {
    "name": "Clicker Cuties - Anime Idler",
    "steam_appid": 3188910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨ Features:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[*] Unlock 20+ Virtual Cuties with unique personalities and stories  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[*] Collect, click, and craft Eggs to hatch rare Cuties</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[*] Unlock full storylines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[*] Lightweight idle design — runs minimized  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[*] Deeper updates coming every few weeks  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍵 Let’s get cozy</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Love comes to those who click in this comfy, chaotic casual idler. Get a random new cutie every 3 hours — or even sooner if you tap fast and use the right strategy. Some cuties are ultra-rare. Some are… legendary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💘 Build your dream collection</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each cutie has her own personality, dialogue, and now — a full story you can unlock as you bond.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet tsunderes, yanderes, dommy mommies, goth gfs, bunnygirls, weirdos, hackers, artists, witches, dreamwalkers, disaster lesbians, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New cuties and features are added with every update. Whether you’re a casual collector or a long-term simp strategist, there’s always someone new to fall for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🥚 Crafting, Clicking, Candies &amp; More</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not just luck — you can now collect shards and craft Eggs to hatch your favorite cuties.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tap to build affection, reduce cooldowns, and earn higher-tier drops. The deeper your account level, the better your chances at scoring rares.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And yes — candies are still here. But they’ve been… rebalanced. 🍬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📖 Storylines &amp; Secrets</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each cutie now has a full storyline you can unlock right in their gallery.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn their pasts, obsessions, heartbreaks, philosophies, and maybe… what they think about <i>you</i>. 😳</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some are funny. Some are spicy. Some are deeply unwell. You’ll love them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌸 Runs on a potato</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicker Cuties runs on just about anything. Minimize it, let it idle in the background, or go full speedclicker — it won’t complain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>~ I can’t wait to meet you, anon ~</i></p>",
